// ** Third Party Components
// import Cleave from 'cleave.js/react'

// ** Reactstrap Imports
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardBody, Form, Label, Input, Button, Row, Col, Select } from 'reactstrap'

const JobRoleEdit = () => {
  return (
    <Card className='card-payment'>
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle tag='h4'>Manage Job Role</CardTitle>
    
      </CardHeader>
      <CardBody>
        <Form className='form' onSubmit={e => e.preventDefault()}>
          <Row>
            <Col sm='12' className='mb-2'>
              <Label className='form-label' for='payment-card-number'>
              Position Name
              </Label>
              <Input placeholder='Eg: Health Care Assis' id='payment-input-name' />
            </Col>
            <Col sm='6' className='mb-2'>
              <Label className='form-label' for='payment-expiry'>
                Expiry
              </Label>
              <Cleave
                className='form-control'
                placeholder='MM / YY'
                options={{ date: true, delimiter: '/', datePattern: ['Y', 'm'] }}
                id='payment-expiry'
              />
            </Col>
            <Col sm='6' className='mb-2'>
              <Label className='form-label' for='payment-cvv'>
              Position short form
              </Label>
              <Input type='number' placeholder='123' id='payment-cvv' />
            </Col>
            <Col sm='12' className='mb-2'>
              <Label className='form-label' for='payment-input-name'>
                Input Name
              </Label>
              <Input placeholder='Curtis Stone' id='payment-input-name' />
            </Col>
            <Col className='d-grid' sm='12'>
              <Button color='success'>Save</Button>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Form>
      </CardBody>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default JobRoleEdit
